♬ <i>Little voice I hear</i> ♬

207
00:26:17.150 --> 00:26:21.160
♬ <i>Yeah maybe</i> ♬

208
00:26:21.160 --> 00:26:25.060
♬ <i>Maybe no</i> ♬

209
00:26:25.060 --> 00:26:29.740
♬ <i>Who’s to say</i> ♬

210
00:26:29.740 --> 00:26:32.890
♬ <i>Slowly drowning in</i> ♬

